---
import SimpleLayout from '../layouts/SimpleLayout.astro';
---

<SimpleLayout title="Start Here" description="The best of my writing, organized by who you are — client, employer, or fellow engineer." url="/start-here">
  <section class="audience-section">
    <div class="audience-card">
      <h2>For Clients</h2>
      <p>Hiring a consultant is a leap of faith. These posts show how I think about solving real problems with AI.</p>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="/blog/2025-02-12-sentinel-objects/">Beyond None: Mastering Sentinel Objects for Cleaner Python Code</a> — Clean code practices that scale</li>
        <li><a href="/blog/2025-02-20-local-git-server/">Why I had to build a Local Git Server</a> — Pragmatic problem-solving under constraints</li>
      </ul>
      <p><a href="/contact" class="cta-link">Interested in working together? Get in touch →</a></p>
    </div>

    <div class="audience-card">
      <h2>For Employers</h2>
      <p>Want to know if I can actually do the work? Here's proof.</p>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="/cv">View my CV →</a></li>
        <li><a href="/blog/2025-02-12-sentinel-objects/">Technical deep-dive: Sentinel Objects</a></li>
        <li><a href="/blog/2025-02-20-local-git-server/">Technical deep-dive: Local Git Server</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="audience-card">
      <h2>For Peers</h2>
      <p>For data scientists and engineers who never stop learning. Neither do I.</p>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="/blog/2025-02-12-sentinel-objects/">Sentinel Objects in Python</a></li>
        <li><a href="/blog/2025-02-20-local-git-server/">Building a Local Git Server</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://github.com/sambaths" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub →</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>
</SimpleLayout>

<style>
  .audience-section {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .audience-card {
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }

  .audience-card h2 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-top: 0;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .audience-card p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .audience-card ul {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .audience-card li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .cta-link {
    display: inline-block;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }
</style>
